cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on object instance segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed SPRNet framework involves introducing a new branch to off-the-shelf one-stage detectors, which requires machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and optimization methods (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed approach, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
